From: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:28:46 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 315/315] FLIGHT: usbcore: attempt to enable remote wakeup for
 root hubs

Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
---
 drivers/usb/core/hub.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/usb/core/hub.c b/drivers/usb/core/hub.c
index 21ac9b464696..e23a5e7cd1ab 100644
--- a/drivers/usb/core/hub.c
+++ b/drivers/usb/core/hub.c
@@ -3479,6 +3479,7 @@ int usb_port_suspend(struct usb_device *udev, pm_message_t msg)
 			if (PMSG_IS_AUTO(msg))
 				goto err_wakeup;
 		}
+		usb_enable_remote_wakeup(udev->bus->root_hub);
 	}
 
 	/* disable USB2 hardware LPM */
